<span id="freeTextContainer2617617683113866125">This lovely story about Jay &amp; Jackapple Joe is one of my all time favourite books. I could read it over &amp; over again.<br/>A story filled with nostalgia, a yearning for wonderful childhood memories, magic and trust. Jay goes on a journey of faith and self discovery, learning how to trust in himself and others, believe in magic and that anything is possible as he once did as a child. With a little help from Joe and his &apos;specials&apos;. <br/>A wonderful heart warming tale that is a pleasure to read.</span>
  <span id="freeText2617617683113866125" style="display:none">This lovely story about Jay &amp; Jackapple Joe is one of my all time favourite books. I could read it over &amp; over again.<br />A story filled with nostalgia, a yearning for wonderful childhood memories, magic and trust. Jay goes on a journey of faith and self discovery, learning how to trust in himself and others, believe in magic and that anything is possible as he once did as a child. With a little help from Joe and his 'specials'. <br />A wonderful heart warming tale that is a pleasure to read.</span>
